    <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › BlueStar › Stove Repair</div>
    <h1>BlueStar Stove Repair in Los Angeles</h1>
    <p class="lede">BlueStar is the Prizer-Painter Stove Works residential brand — independent family-owned since 1880, hand-built at Blandon, Pennsylvania, with residential production adapted from the company's commercial-stove heritage. That's the service-defining detail: BlueStar is one of the few remaining independent family-owned stove makers in the luxury category, Nova Burners are open-burner (not sealed) carried over from commercial platform, 25,000 BTU signature output is the highest in the residential luxury category (3k over Viking's 23k, 5k over Wolf's 20k), and the 750+ RAL color program is the widest in luxury. In LA, BlueStar concentrates in chef-owned households, design-forward custom kitchens, and Bel Air + Beverly Hills ultra-luxury remodels where the 25k Nova Burner + 750-color flexibility + Precious Metal trim options are specifically valued. Same-day dispatch, $89 residential diagnostic waived with the repair.</p>
